File Permissions:
------------------

Create Group
- groupadd new_group


Add Group Members
- useradd user_name new_group

Adjust rwx Directory and File Permissions
- chgrp: change the group of the file
  chgrp group_name /directory
- chmod: change permissions of file or directory
  - use g for group permissions, o for other permissions, u for user/owner
  - r is for read, w is for write, x is for execute
  - + is for add permissions, - is for subtracting permissions
  chmod g+rwx /directory/file
- chown: change the owner of the file
  chown user_name /directory/file
